<span id="freeTextContainer9167907534613113142">let us all take a brief moment of silence and remember the old me, the person i was before i read this book; because by the end of the story, i became someone new and improved.<br/><br/>i knew this was going to be a 5 star read within the first couple of chapters, but the absolute magnitude of this story is truly astonishing. and im finding it difficult to adequately describe the raw sincerity and intense emotional pull of this book. <br/><br/>i have never used the word <i>‘unputdownable’</i> before in a review, but maybe</span>
  <span id="freeText9167907534613113142" style="display:none">let us all take a brief moment of silence and remember the old me, the person i was before i read this book; because by the end of the story, i became someone new and improved.<br /><br />i knew this was going to be a 5 star read within the first couple of chapters, but the absolute magnitude of this story is truly astonishing. and im finding it difficult to adequately describe the raw sincerity and intense emotional pull of this book. <br /><br />i have never used the word <i>‘unputdownable’</i> before in a review, but maybe thats because i knew i was saving it for this one - for a story that teaches through tender feelings and the fragility of human connection, for a story that makes the reader not only examine their life but the lives of those around them, for a story that makes the heart grow and love. <br /><br />this is such a special book and one i now hold dear. <br /><br /><b>↠ <i>5 stars</i></b></span>
